lead_paragraph: A USA Gymnastics appeals panel rejected a petition by the former Olympic gold medalist Dominique Moceanu to compete at next week’s national championships. Moceanu, attempting a comeback at age 24, competed in the vault and the floor exercise last month at a qualifying event and finished among the bottom five in both events.
